        <div class="mt-6 h-px w-16 bg-primary-400"></div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/85">We use 88 Restaurants to manage online reservations at {{ client.name }}. We are currently accepting online reservations for parties of up to 10.</p>
